videos.description: 1H (17:37) WICH Zach Brown made Layup. Assisted by Ron Baker.
videos.headline: Ron Baker takes it away and pitches ahead to Zach Brown who cuts through the lane for a nice left-handed layup

Zach Brown forces the turnover and finishes with a dunk

videos.headline: Jakob Poeltl gets the rebound on one end, hustles down the court and sneaks in back door for a layup

videos.description: 2H (14:18) WICH Shaquille Morris made Dunk. Assisted by Ron Baker.
videos.headline: Ron Baker continues to be unselfish with the ball, gives a quick pass inside to Shaquille Morris who dunks it in

videos.description: Wichita State's Shaquille Morris with the big rejection at the rim to start a fast break from the Shockers, but Utah's Brekkott Chapman returns the favor with a big time swat of his own.
videos.headline: There's a block party going on in Wichita

videos.description: 2H (10:47) WICH Markis McDuffie made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Fred VanVleet.
videos.headline: Markis McDuffie beats the shot clock for his fourth three of the game
Larry Krystkowiak wants a defensive interference call, gets a technical instead

videos.description: 2H (3:57) WICH Rauno Nurger made Layup. Assisted by Fred VanVleet.
videos.headline: Wichita State keeps on hustling despite a double digit lead, Shockers grab back to back offensive rebounds and finish off with a layup

videos.description: 2H (0:20) WICH Conner Frankamp made Three Point Jumper.
videos.headline: Conner Frankcamp pulls up for a three point jumper and the arena erupts as Wichita State pulls the upset
